article.description: — Joel Soriano scored 16 points as St. John's beat Holy Cross 91-45 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Soriano guides St. John's to 91-45 victory over Holy Cross
article.linkText: Soriano guides St. John's to 91-45 victory over Holy Cross
article.story: NEW YORK -- — Joel Soriano scored 16 points as St. John's beat Holy Cross 91-45 on Saturday night. Soriano also contributed six rebounds for the Red Storm (4-2). RJ Luis added 14 points while going 6 of 12 from the field, and they also had three steals. Jordan Dingle had 11 points and shot 5 for 8, including 1 for 4 from beyond the arc. The Crusaders (2-5) were led by Caleb Kenney, who posted eight points. Joseph Octave added seven points for Holy Cross. Joe Nugent also had six points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
